{"id": "1480093685944422580", "channel_id": "1480093685944422580", "type": 0, "author_id": "473419057731862528", "author_name": "xagarath", "author_bot": false, "content": "Seeing from the new patch notes that auto-battle will be disabled from character trials means there is now no easy way to complete the 50-card daily mission.\nWhy force players to grind through random battles every day? Many of us have limited free time, and do not want to log into a game every day unless we can complete daily tasks on auto.", "timestamp": "2026-03-08T06:43:53.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}, {"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480096093499949127", "channel_id": "1480093685944422580", "type": 0, "author_id": "514145255923253272", "author_name": "milliampere_0237", "author_bot": false, "content": "It's personally very easy. You can play traphase and hit the quota or you can play/borrow a e3 castor that loves giving onyx plumes (or oe, that's even better)", "timestamp": "2026-03-08T06:53:27.546000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
