{"id": "1480174987120869621", "channel_id": "1480093685944422580", "type": 0, "author_id": "618475034465533954", "author_name": "silencio3507", "author_bot": false, "content": "I rarely use auto (only on easy train to gain unlocks), but I see no point in this change? Why even add auto to then remove it from some sections of the game? If the players wants to auto, they should have that options. It's not like those trials are good at teaching what characters do, some of them are long and tedious.", "timestamp": "2026-03-08T12:06:57.251000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
